name: London 2012 Olympic Print
description:
A beautiful hand-illustrated print to commemorate the London 2012 Olympic Games.

Printed on high quality Somerset Velvet Enhanced paper. This is a nice heavy paper stock with the look and feel of watercolour paper.

Size: 297mm x 420mm (approx).

Also available as a framed print (UK only). All frames are hand-made to order. Please enquire for further details.

The print will be shipped in a strong cardboard tube to ensure it arrives safely.

//Special offer for July & August - free shipping! Use code 2012OLYMPICS at the checkout//

name: Diamond Jubilee Bone China Mug
description:
A beautiful bone China commemorative mug printed with an original hand-drawn portrait of the Queen and Diamond Jubilee banner. This would make a lovely gift to or keepsake to mark the Queen's Diamond Jubilee.

Features illustration of The Queen on one side, and a Diamond Jubilee banner in blue on the reverse.

Packaged securely and boxed to ensure no nasty accidents.

name: Diamond Jubilee Tea Towel
description:
100% cotton tea towel, printed with an original hand-drawn portrait of the Queen and Diamond Jubilee banner. A sweet little gift to commemorate Her Majesty's Diamond Jubilee.

Size: 48cm (w) x 78 cm (h). Hemmed two sides only.

Made from superior grade cotton and super-absorbent, it would make a welcome addition to your kitchen.

This tea towel has been woven and sewn in Britain, and is proud to proclaim its loyalty with a Union Jack label.

name: Girl & Bird pocket mirror
description:
Sweet little pocket mirror, featuring an original hand-drawn illustration of a girl and hummingbird. Fits perfectly in your bag or purse.

Mirror measures 58mm across, and comes packaged in a little clear bag.

All mirrors are safely wrapped in bubble wrap before being sent via Royal Mail.
